{"tid":834662,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"撞你老母咩？你把口啞架？","createTime":"2018-09-24T10:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T16:58:51.000Z","uid":23046,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4d86197e1e4a6dd2219697f5e6826816209ca2f0","tid":834662,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，中秋個撚個都趕時間番屋企架啦<br />\n得你一個趕咩？<br />\n你出左聲人地唔讓比你都算<br />\n直接係度撞黎撞去<br />\n又係度推<br />\n咁撚多人<br />\n推跌左幾撚危險？<br />\n如果你屋企人比人推跌左<br />\n比人踩到會點<br />\n屌你老母最多係d死廢老<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">祝你比人撞撚左落月台</span></span>"},{"pid":"698407fce1858df857e7bfda5df530589940138c","tid":834662,"uid":16061,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定係一路睇電話一路行個啲撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faea27a326f7ccec0192040848b629e1839b2fca","tid":834662,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:32:26.000Z","msg":"出聲屌佢囉毒撚"},{"pid":"06927feec8fbacba384004f75a14c0dd32c2f7d3","tid":834662,"uid":128741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"faea27a326f7ccec0192040848b629e1839b2fca","tid":834662,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:32:26.000Z","msg":"出聲屌佢囉毒撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"講就凶狠 做就碌撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9513c72ae1cc10b6f2a8d62c2a5d25be566bb14f","tid":834662,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪又係唔出聲"},{"pid":"8a63776dbd55cb0d6bcb90efb25cd548860ab044","tid":834662,"uid":5460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:34:34.000Z","msg":"用個 keyboard 車鳩佢"},{"pid":"97d4588aded16363ee4f0d5dce176fe8bfdf338c","tid":834662,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy